high_descs: Head to the kitchen countertop in front.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn to the potato on the right.
Put the knife on the plate.
Pick up the plate from the counter.
Turn around to reach the diningtable with the microwave.
Put the plate on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Put the potato on the plate on the diningtable.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the countertop.
Take the knife from the table.
Cut the potato into pieces using the knife.
Put the knife on the plate.
Take the plate with knife from the table.
Turn around and go near the diningtable.
Put the plate with knife on the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Placed the potato with knife on the diningtable.

high_descs: Turn left then turn right to the countertop.
Take the knife from the counter top.
Turn right to the potato on the counter top.
Put the knife on the plate on the counter top.
Take the plate along with knife.
Turn around then turn right to the diningtable
Place the plate along with knife near to the diningtable.
anns.task_desc: Take the Potato along with Plate and Place the Potato along with Plate near to the DiningTable
